name: #12. DONNY “THE DRAPES” MCNALLY
description:
Some bunnies just got style. Some don't. That's just the way of the world. But Drapes, Drapes oozes it. He makes a room look good. Hell, just by hanging with him give you more style.

"The more you take, the more you leave behind. What am I?"
"Feed me and I live, yet give me a drink and I die"
"What has hands but can not clap?"

'r' toggles auto-rotate.
